docs.lead_paragraph: After most of the week had been passed in a quiet and composed state, with business at a minimum and rate fluctuations narrow, the French franc weakened suddenly at the week-end in the foreign exchange market and was carried down to 6.60 1/2 cents at the close, the lowest since June 25.

docs.lead_paragraph: Plans for the first aerial cruise trips -- fourteen and twenty-one day all-expense flights to Rio de Janeiro -- were disclosed yesterday by Pan American Airways. Sixteen such flights will be made from Miami, the first to start on Aug. 16 and each Sunday thereafter until the series has been completed.
docs.abstract: Announces 16 all-expense cruises between Miami and Rio de Janeiro, beginning Aug 16
